WEBVTT

00:04:57.897 --> 00:05:00.270
And so I stopped
using my voice in my work.

00:05:01.984 --> 00:05:05.750
Since then, I've thought a lot
about what it means to be normal.

00:05:07.218 --> 00:05:09.236
And I've come to understand

00:05:09.260 --> 00:05:12.639
that "normal" has a lot to do
with expectations.

00:05:13.307 --> 00:05:14.836
Let me give you an example.

00:05:14.860 --> 00:05:16.190
I came across this story

00:05:16.214 --> 00:05:18.480
about the Ancient Greek writer, Homer.

00:05:18.504 --> 00:05:21.753
Now, Homer mentions
very few colors in his writing.

00:05:22.650 --> 00:05:24.255
And even when he does,

00:05:24.279 --> 00:05:26.317
he seems to get them quite a bit wrong.

00:05:26.936 --> 00:05:30.228
For example, the sea
is described as wine red,